beer.beer_description: Our GABS 2020 beer. Inspired by the Viennese "Sachertorte" cake, we've added chocolate and apricot to a luscious Imperial Stout. A late boil addition of Simcoe imparts a slight earthy bitterness. Let this dessert-in-a-can warm slightly to let the aromas leap from the glass! Enjoy!
